parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of brake lines can cause a loss of braking power, leading to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: Brake pedal feels soft or spongy
brake pedal sticks to the floor

brake pedal has a delayed return to its normal position
brake pedal has a sudden loss of pressure

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission and other components can cause accidents or injuries.
